dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially, and by shading.
2 bar scales on map, given in "Milliaria Germanica communia" and "Milliaria Gallica communia."
Decorative cartouche with shield and cherubs; compass rose with figure.
Shows topography, lakes and rivers, vegetation.
Appears in Blaeu's Theatrum orbis terrarum, sive, atlas novus, Spanish edition: Nuevo atlas o teatro del mundo, ... En Amsterdam, A costa en casa de Juan Blaeu, 1659-1672.
